haqeeqat ( hindi : हक़ीक़त , urdu : حقیقت , translation : reality ) is a 1964 hindi war-film directed by chetan anand .   the film stars balraj sahni , dharmendra , priya rajvansh , sudhir , sanjay khan and vijay anand .   the music is by madan mohan and the lyrics by kaifi azmi .   the movie was based on the 1962 sino-indian war .   it won the national film award for second best feature film in 1965 .   the film was screened retrospective on august 12 , 2016 at the independence day film festival jointly presented by the indian directorate of film festivals and ministry of defense , commemorating 70th indian independence day .